      • reportFault

        protected void reportFault​(SOAPFaultInfo fault,
                           StreamingHandlerState state)
        Note that a call to StreamingHandlerState.resetResponse() creates a new SAAJ SOAPMessage for the response with the FI flag based on the SOAPMessageContext state. This is needed for content negotiation.
